The '''Verbund Casimcea Wind Farm''' is an operational [[wind power]] project located in [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It consists of 88 individual [[wind turbine]]s  with a nominal output 2.5 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each which will deliver up to 540 GWh of power, enough to power over 350,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately €380 million.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.business24.ro/companii/investitii/verbund-a-investit-380-milioane-de-euro-in-parcul-eolian-casimcea-1529781|title=Verbund a investit 380 milioane de euro in parcul eolian Casimcea|date=6 June 2013|publisher=business24.ro|language=Romanian|accessdate=10 December 2013}}</ref>

